545
00:41:15,805 --> 00:41:17,796
變化是無窮的
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}There were many changes.{\r}

546
00:41:17,907 --> 00:41:20,967
有些看得到 有些看不到
