548
00:41:25,482 --> 00:41:27,450
還有很多其他的事物
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}along with other things.{\r}

549
00:41:28,751 --> 00:41:31,481
我感覺很棒
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}I felt pretty good, considering.{\r}

550
00:41:32,555 --> 00:41:35,217
親愛的 痛
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}Darling, the pain.{\r}

551
00:41:35,325 --> 00:41:37,850
好的 媽媽 我去叫護士
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}All right, Mom, I'll get the nurse.{\r}

552
00:41:40,396 --> 00:41:43,058
看看風眼 這是強烈颶風
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}Look at this eye. This is a major hurricane,{\r}

553
00:41:43,633 --> 00:41:46,158
颶風移動不快 伴隨最大持續風…
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}a slow hurricane, with maximum sustained winds of...{\r}

554
00:41:46,269 --> 00:41:48,100
感覺不好？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}Not doing too good?{\r}

555
00:41:48,972 --> 00:41:52,237
似乎沒人知道該走還是該留
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}Nobody seems to know whether to stay or leave.{\r}

556
00:41:52,342 --> 00:41:54,640
都會過去的
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}I'm gonna ride it out.{\r}

557
00:41:54,744 --> 00:41:57,611
好了 讓她舒服點
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}There. That should make things much easier.{\r}

558
00:42:01,050 --> 00:42:04,247
道過別了嗎？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}Have you had a chance to say your goodbyes?{\r}

559
00:42:04,354 --> 00:42:07,846
我父親等我弟弟從博格市回來 等了四個小時 
