560
00:42:07,957 --> 00:42:09,925
想見他最後一面
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}Couldn't go without him.{\r}

561
00:42:10,460 --> 00:42:13,122
- 她看上去很安詳 - 是啊
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}- She seems like a sweet woman. - Yeah.{\r}

562
00:42:13,796 --> 00:42:15,491
我應該多陪陪她的…
